subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which dynasty is associated with the formation of the Rao Kalyanji State?
question_hi: राव कालियांजी के स्थानीय स्थानीय भाग के लिए किस नवाचार्य संस्था संबंधी है?
explanation_en: The Kachwaha Rajputs were associated with the formation of the Bhillamiya Dynasty in Rajasthan. The Bhillamiya Dynasty ruled Rajasthan during the medieval period. The Tikamgarh Rajputs were prominent during the Marwar Sultanate while the Bhils are a tribal community and not directly related to the formation of any specific dynasty.
